    "description": "Welcome to a private gated home that combines exceptional design with smart home technology, rarely found at this price point. This is easily one of the best values currently offered in the Hollywood Hills. Built from the studs up with fire safety in mind, the home is designed with thoughtful room flow and seamless indoor-outdoor living, featuring beautiful natural light, expansive glass doors, and high-quality wide-plank wood floors.The spacious primary suite includes two closets and a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub positioned to capture clear views of the Hollywood Sign, the Santa Monica Mountains, and Mount Baldy. Two additional guest bedrooms provide comfortable accommodations, while the detached fourth bedroom with kitchenette and bath is ideal for guests or extended family.Additional highlights include a 480-bottle wine cellar, Dolby Atmos home theater, upgraded gym, bar area, and a detached guest house. A range of tech-forward upgrades includes a Crestron smart home system with iPad controls, remote-controlled blinds, custom garage doors, fully paid solar panels, and a separate guardhouse with its own bathroom and more than 15 security cameras for added privacy and peace of mind.Thoughtful improvements such as earthquake retrofitting, new sewer lines, advanced water filtration, fire-retardant sprinklers, and instant-heat shower systems provide both comfort and efficiency, making this home a smart and secure investment.Entertain effortlessly with a saltwater heated pool, generous fire pit, built-in BBQ, retractable patio sunroof, and a 60-light landscape system that transforms the space at night. The grounds are primarily planted with long-lasting perennials, a major investment that enhances year-round beauty while reducing ongoing plant replacement costs. This hidden gem offers a sanctuary-like setting with layered landscaping, vibrant flowers, and fruit trees including avocado, guava, pomegranate, citrus, and more. The grounds are alive with butterflies, hummingbirds, and natural beauty throughout the year.Three tranquil water features, including a koi and turtle pond, a Buddha fountain, and a lush plant wall, create a peaceful and inspiring outdoor experience. Located just moments from Runyon Canyon's scenic trails and views of the Hollywood Sign, this unique home offers the perfect balance of privacy, convenience, and lifestyle. Luxury, location, and comfort all come together in a rare offering that truly stands out in today's market.",
