    "description": "Perched at the pinnacle of one of Brentwood's most coveted cul-de-sacs, this custom modern trophy estate is nothing short of a masterpiece - where golden California light pours through soaring floor-to-ceiling glass, wrapping every inch of interior in a warm, cinematic glow that has to be seen to be believed. Commanding breathtaking panoramic views stretching from Downtown Los Angeles to the coastline and Crestwood Hills, the architecture dissolves the line between indoors and out, with disappearing glass panels that seamlessly marry the dramatic wrap-around deck, lush surroundings, and impeccably curated interiors into one intoxicating living experience. Entertain in the sleek chef's kitchen and sprawling dining room, then let the sun-drenched views from the oversized living room take your breath away. The primary suite is a private sanctuary, complete with a spa-inspired bath and walk-in closet, while four additional en-suite bedrooms offer the same effortless luxury. Descend to the lower level to discover a state-of-the-art home theater, glass-enclosed wine room, and gym. Outside, a dramatic infinity pool reflects the sky like a mirror, flanked by a lush grassy pad perfectly suited for soaking in the Southern California sun. This is Brentwood at its most extraordinary - a luminous trophy that lives as beautifully as it photographs.",
